          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "On an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object where "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1624595-lowlightboostsupported"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", a special low light boost mode may be engaged to improve image quality. When the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "automaticallyEnablesLowLightBoostWhenAvailable"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property is set to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the capture device switches at its discretion to a special boost mode under low light. When the scene becomes sufficiently lit, the device switches back to normal operation. An "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " that supports this feature may only engage boost mode for certain source formats or resolutions."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The default value of this property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Setting this property throws an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsinvalidargumentexception"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1624595-lowlightboostsupported"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object must be locked for configuration using "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1387810-lockforconfiguration"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " before clients can set this method, otherwise an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsgenericexception"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is thrown."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Clients may observe changes to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1624602-lowlightboostenabled"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property using "
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "title": "Key-value observing",
              "destination": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/General/Conceptual/DevPedia-CocoaCore/KVO.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40008195-CH16"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to know when the boost mode engages. The switch between normal operation and low light boost mode may drop one or more video frames."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
